:[19907,99275,1329820,2067202,2613675],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"这个问题的初衷，其实是将“为别人付出劳动与精力能够拿到的金钱”与“提升自己所付出的劳动与精力能够产生的成果”进行比较而产生的疑问 就是我突然发现在你没有一个能稳定获取可观的金钱回报的工作的时候，你为别人做一些回报性不大的兼职的时候，为什么不去提升自己，为自己“打工”呢。自己给自己开工资？ 然后我思考了一下，这是不是一种对自己能否产生价值的一种怀疑呢？是一种不自信呢？ 给别人打工，也许结果就是一个固定的，你一定能获取到的。 但是给自己打工，你没有一个判断标准去明确你能获得什么？某种程度上说，就是你对自己没有一个非常肯定的一个自信，去认为自己一定能通过消耗这个给自己发的工资而产生令自己满意的价值。 我想听听别人怎么想"},"attached_info":"Cj8ItZ/Ujdv//6YqEAMaCTExMDQwMDY1MiCglvW2BjAAOG9ABXIJNjY2NTUyMjA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"89 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6ca1373742725f38b12577c4cbedc4aa_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1726031934.499078","card_id":"Q_666499239","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":666499239,"title":"英雄联盟13周年策划面对面环节里，设计师表示致命节奏将回归，如何评价LOL设计师的专业能力和工作水平？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/666499239","type":"question","created":1725722155,"answer_count":23,"follower_count":26,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[358,664,18427,70885,80713],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"Cj8ItZ/Ujdv//6YqEAMaCTExMDM4ODg5NSCr3PG2BjAAOBpABnIJNjY2NDk5MjM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4d88f5a2a38d21e30082560dcf356f7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1726031934.501086","card_id":"Q_661406189","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{